## Disclaimer

This software is designed specifically for OpenWrt routers and network diagnostic purposes. It is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with their local network policies and regulations.

The software includes network monitoring capabilities that may collect system and network performance data. Users should review and understand what data is collected and how it is used before deployment in production environments.

